Package: dtsus
Title: Download, Index and Process DATASUS DBC Microdata
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lucas", "Fontes", , "lucasrodriguesfontes@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Raquel", "Schneider", , "raquelschneider03@gmail.com", role = "aut")
)
Description: Provides tools to discover, index, download and process public health microdata from the DATASUS FTP server ('ftp.datasus.gov.br'). Functions support file listing, batch downloads, reading DBC files, filtering records, selecting variables and exporting results to DBC or RData formats. Designed for reproducible workflows when working with large Brazilian health information systems.
